	* message.el (message-bury): Use `window-dedicated-p'.

2004-10-10  Reiner Steib  <Reiner.Steib@gmx.de>

	* gnus-sum.el: Mention that multibyte characters don't work as marks.

	* gnus.el (message-y-or-n-p): Autoload.

